<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 2em;">
  <div class="container" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        This page explains what information Eva Tours and Travels collects
        when you book a cab or contact us, and how we use it.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--ink-soft);">
        Last updated: July 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card" style="max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.2em;">

      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Eva Tours and Travels is a taxi service owned and operated by
        <%= business.owner %>, serving <%= business.location %> and
        surrounding routes. This policy covers information collected
        through this website (<%= siteUrl %>) and through direct phone
        or WhatsApp bookings.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you book a cab or send an enquiry, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name and mobile number</li>
        <li>Pickup and drop locations</li>
        <li>Travel date and trip type (local, outstation, airport, etc.)</li>
        <li>Any additional details you choose to share in the booking form or over a call</li>
        <li>Your email address, if you contact us by email</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not collect payment card details through this website —
        payments are made directly to the driver by cash or UPI at the
        end of a trip.
      </p>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the details you share only to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Confirm and assign a driver for your booking</li>
        <li>Contact you about pickup timing or changes to your trip</li>
        <li>Quote and agree a fare before the trip begins</li>
        <li>Follow up on feedback or complaints, if any</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not use your information for unrelated marketing, and we
        do not sell or rent your personal information to any third party.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
      <p>
        Your name, phone number, and pickup/drop details are shared only
        with the driver assigned to your trip, so far as needed to
        complete that booking. We may also disclose information if
        required to do so by law or by a government authority.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Cookies &amp; Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        This website embeds a Google Maps view on the Contact page to
        show our service area. Google may set its own cookies when that
        map loads, governed by Google's own privacy policy. Aside from
        this, the site does not currently use tracking or advertising
        cookies.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        Booking enquiries submitted through this website are used to
        contact you about your trip and are not stored in a public
        database. We take reasonable steps to keep phone numbers and
        booking details confidential, but no method of transmission over
        the internet is completely secure.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Your Choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can ask us to delete any enquiry details we hold about you,
        or ask what information we have, by contacting us using the
        details below. Since bookings are mostly arranged by phone, you
        can also simply let us know verbally when you call.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our services are intended for use by adults booking transport.
        We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time as our services
        change. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page will
        reflect the most recent revision.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        For any privacy-related questions, reach out to
        <%= business.owner %> directly:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+91<%= business.phone1 %>"><%= business.phone1 %></a> / <a href="tel:+91<%= business.phone2 %>"><%= business.phone2 %></a></li>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:<%= business.email %>"><%= business.email %></a></li>
        <li>Service area: <%= business.location %></li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-ink">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <h2>Questions about your data?</h2>
    <p>Call or email us any time — we're happy to explain.</p>
    <a href="tel:+91<%= business.phone1 %>" class="btn btn-primary"><%= business.phone1 %></a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>